articles.author: Jacob Shamsian, Brent D. Griffiths
articles.title: Georgia court document said Trump would get RICO charges
articles.description: The court document — which was removed from the court website — indicated Trump would be charged under 13 different statutes.
articles.content: The Fulton County Courts website briefly posted and then removed a document indicating former President Donald Trump would be charged under 13 different criminal statutes for his efforts to overturn … [+2673 chars]
